!theme plain
title Epic 8 - US30: Guest Passive Bonuses
class Party {
    + get_active_bonuses() : Set[str]
}
class GuestDataRegistry {
    - _guest_data : Dict[str, GuestData]
    + get_guest_bonuses(guest_id : str) : Set[str]
}
note right: Registry Pattern
class CombatRules {
    + apply_guest_bonuses(party : Party)
}
Party --> GuestDataRegistry : queries
CombatRules --> Party : applies bonuses
@enduml